              "[
                \"\",
                {\"text\":\"§lEntry #1: The Meeting
\"},
                {\"text\":\"I just met an amazing woman! She’s beautiful, in her bright red obi.\"},
                {\"text\":\"Plus, hearing about the wonderful scenes she’s seen has inspired me to learn the skills I need to explore. I’d love to visit her home someday.\"}
              ]"
            ],
            title:Journal,
            author:Unkown,
            display:{Lore:["Found in the Haunted Manor"]}
            }

{
          pages:[
              "[
                \"\",
                {\"text\":\"§lEntry #2: Remodeling
\"},
                {\"text\":\"It’s been a few weeks now, and things are going swimmingly. Can’t be happier! She gets along well with all of my servants.\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"My cat’s still a little bit scared of her, but he’s always been timid. My love has even asked for a room to remodel! I can’t wait to see what she does with it.\"}
              ]"
            ],
            title:Journal,
            author:Unkown,
            display:{Lore:["Found in the Haunted Manor"]}
            }

{
          pages:[
              "[
                \"\",
                {\"text\":\"§lEntry #3: The Screaming
\"},
                {\"text\":\"It's been a few days now, but the screaming won’t stop.\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"I don’t want to go down and see what’s happening. I don’t want to know. She says everything is alright. I’ll trust her.\"}
              ]"
            ],
            title:Journal,
            author:Unkown,
            display:{Lore:["Found in the Haunted Manor"]}
            }

{
          pages:[
              "[
                \"\",
                {\"text\":\"§lEntry #4: I'm Sorry
\"},
                {\"text\":\"I’m sorry, I’m sorry, I’m sorry. I let a monster into our house. Delivered my own men to it on a silver platter.\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"It gave me a gift the other day. Dennis’s head, wrapped in a present. I had to swallow my own vomit.\"}
              ]"
            ],
            title:Journal,
            author:Unkown,
            display:{Lore:["Found in the Haunted Manor"]}
            }

{
          pages:[
              "[
                \"\",
                {\"text\":\"§lEntry #5: Trapped
\"},
                {\"text\":\"I told it to follow me to the basement. That more of my servants were there. I don’t know why it listened. I don’t know why it followed me. But I caught it. I trapped it.\"}
              ]"
            ],
            title:Journal,
            author:Unkown,
            display:{Lore:["Found in the Haunted Manor"]}
            }

{
          pages:[
              "[
                \"\",
                {\"text\":\"§lEntry #6: The End
\"},
                {\"text\":\"I’ve had to dig so many graves over the past week. With each one, I feel like there is one more soul dragging at my back.\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"I can’t sleep these days. And sometimes, I swear I can see her face, it’s beautiful and monstrous face through my window. I’m sure she’s cursing me, from her own hell. Don’t worry. I’ll join soon.\"}
              ]"
            ],
            title:Journal,
            author:Unkown,
            display:{Lore:["Found in the Haunted Manor"]}
            }
